Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.44,0:52:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh\Nmirroring therefore results also in
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.55,0:52:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,constraint and constraint. Uh because\Nthat which you mirror may also be on the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.96,0:52:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,positive uh beneficial uh uh human side.\NAll of this results that there is a
