Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.52,0:52:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So ethical concern for others is not\Njust religion or just not uh taught
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.55,0:52:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,morality but it's imitative.\NSo I think that's a very interesting way
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.31,0:53:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,in which we we call learning by example\Nserving by example.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.11,0:53:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh certainly uh in the military I\Nremember uh it was very important you
