Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.52,0:54:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the macak monkey quickly learns this\None gives you a larger amount of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.88,0:54:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Left to his own devices, the macak\Nmonkey will always push the big more
