Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.83,0:54:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,here. So, he goes for the three\Ncheeseburgers.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.83,0:54:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you put another monkey in another\Ncage right next to this macock monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.80,0:54:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And every time this macock monkey pushes\Nthe big wind lever and gets a bigger
