Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.24,1:00:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So sigman Ford was like great grandpa\Nand u all these things can be poo pooed
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.35,1:00:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in theory but experientially it's quite\Ndifferent. Anybody here been through
