Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.07,1:02:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so funny. I could hardly keep\Nkeep from laughing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.72,1:02:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. So Freud postulated these two\Nprimary two primary instincts because if
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.72,1:02:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you watch carefully you'll see people\Nare very entranced by death. I mean
