Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.11,1:02:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and millions watched it just fascinated\Nwatching somebody die watching their
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.72,1:02:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,head get cut off. So people are just\Nfascinated by death in all of its. So
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.79,1:02:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the attraction of death, you\Nknow, both conscious and unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.68,1:02:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NThe next one we're going to talk about
