Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.48,1:34:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the underlying innocence the inner child\Nthe inner child within Adam and Eve that
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.28,1:34:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eve\Ntrusting like a little child trust his
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.28,1:34:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,mother. Trusted the serpent says, "Trust\Nme, trust me, trust me." And Eve uh
