Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.15,1:34:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore\Nuh four warns you not to disobey. So it
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.28,1:34:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,could be rationalized differently and\NI'll ask him next time I see him.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.88,1:34:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,God, what was it?\NHe'll tell me. So,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.48,1:34:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,those who serve the Lord are served by\Nthe Lord. Those who serve the Lord are
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.36,1:35:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,served by the Lord. Those who call upon\NJesus as their savior, Jesus be Jesus
