Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.12,1:35:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot refuse you\Nthat is that is a fact
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.36,1:35:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the lord cannot refuse you when you\Nworship the lord when you say unto thee
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.76,1:36:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,oh lord\NAll glory and thanks be now and forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.60,1:36:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Lord God cannot refuse you. Cannot\Nrefuse you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.15,1:36:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that encouraging?\NAnybody here doesn't want to believe
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.56,1:36:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that God is the author of all existence?\NGlory be to the Lord as the source of
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.40,1:36:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,our existence, also the source of our\Nsalvation.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.63,1:36:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We give thanks for the great saviors of\Ntime, the Buddha, the Jesus Christ, the
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.84,1:36:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the great the great ones of of all time\Nbecause they speak for us before the
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.44,1:36:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,father. They speak for us before the\Nfather. And if I make any mistakes, if
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.32,1:36:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,any of the teachings I've taught in\Nthese classes is in error, I promise
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.88,1:36:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you, I will speak for you before the\Nfather that it was my teaching, my
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.08,1:36:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,error, my shortcoming\Nuh to own to own the source of the error
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.00,1:37:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,uh is here.\NAnd uh so that's what we ask of a
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.88,1:37:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual teacher that we don't ask the\Ncommitment of the student to the
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.11,1:37:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,teacher. We ask the commitment of the\Nteacher to the student.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.80,1:37:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A classic is you're supposed to worship\Nthe teacher and bringing him all kinds
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.96,1:37:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of things like this and pack stack it up\Naround him.
