Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.04,1:37:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,your agilation and your worship and your\Nflowers and your fruits and all such
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.23,1:37:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,being complete and total in yourself the\Nteacher had has no needs whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.23,1:37:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the obligation is but from the\Nteacher to the student from the teacher
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.32,1:37:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to teach this the truth to the highest\Nlevel he is capable of teaching. So the
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.67,1:37:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,commitment is from the teacher to the\Nstudent and not the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.84,1:38:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it had been seen the other way\Naround, the number of people who become
